textBeforeTable: All costs associated with purchasing land in the form of an easement. Easements give the City the right to use another persons property. Record in this account such costs as appraisal fees, closing fees, title fees, environmental surveys and legal fees. Fees may apply to donated assets in which case these fees should be recorded in this account.
